Query: How to embed dashboard code from Tableau Public into Google Cloud to deploy in an app

ChatGPT said:
You can deploy your Tableau Public dashboard on Google Cloud using a simple Flask web app. This will allow you to host the dashboard in a web application with a custom domain if needed.

ðŸš€ Steps to Deploy a Tableau Dashboard on Google Cloud
Step 1: Get Your Tableau Public Embed Code
Publish your dashboard on Tableau Public.

Click on "Share", then copy the embed code (it looks like this):

html
Copy
Edit
<iframe src="https://public.tableau.com/views/YOUR_DASHBOARD" width="100%" height="600px"></iframe>
Step 2: Create a Flask Web App
You'll deploy a simple Python Flask app to display the dashboard.

Install Flask (if not installed):

bash
Copy
Edit
pip install flask
Create app.py with this code:

python
Copy
Edit
from flask import Flask, render_template

app = Flask(__name__)

@app.route("/")
def home():
    return render_template("index.html")

if __name__ == "__main__":
    app.run(host="0.0.0.0", port=8080)
Create a templates/index.html file:

html
Copy
Edit
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tableau Dashboard</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>My Tableau Dashboard</h1>
    <iframe src="https://public.tableau.com/views/YOUR_DASHBOARD" width="100%" height="800px"></iframe>
</body>
</html>
Step 3: Deploy to Google Cloud Run
Install Google Cloud SDK if you havenâ€™t:

bash
Copy
Edit
curl https://sdk.cloud.google.com | bash
gcloud init
Enable Cloud Run and set a project:

bash
Copy
Edit
gcloud config set project YOUR_PROJECT_ID
gcloud services enable run.googleapis.com
Create a Dockerfile for deployment:

dockerfile
Copy
Edit
FROM python:3.9
WORKDIR /app
COPY . .
RUN pip install flask
CMD ["python", "app.py"]
Deploy to Cloud Run:

bash
Copy
Edit
gcloud builds submit --tag gcr.io/YOUR_PROJECT_ID/tableau-app
gcloud run deploy tableau-app --image gcr.io/YOUR_PROJECT_ID/tableau-app --platform managed --allow-unauthenticated
Step 4: Access Your App
Once deployed, Google Cloud Run will give you a URL like:
ðŸ”— https://tableau-app-xyz.a.run.app/

This will display your Tableau dashboard in a hosted web app.

